{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"Root cause (proven, joe-debug): 3 stale probe assertions. (1) line 145 'edit $BUG --tags=probe,edited' -> engine now errors exit 1 'Error: --tags is no longer an edit field. Use --set-tags / --add-tag / --remove-tag' (confirmed in isolated store). (2) line 147 'edit priority persisted' fails as COLLATERAL: --tags makes the whole edit command error before priority persists. (3) line 276 'show and list element have identical key sets' fails because show legitimately includes 'comments'+'description' keys that list omits by design (confirmed: comm shows exactly {comments, description} present in show, absent in list). Fix: line 145 use --set-tags; line 276 assert list-keys are a subset of show-keys (or that the only diff is comments+description), not identical."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782779379368457001,"uuid":"2e7985dc-4114-4ca4-bdca-47f60dcf0586"}